%%{init: {'theme': 'forest'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor FW as Firmware
  participant API as Go API (device-open)
  participant DB as Postgres/Timescale

  FW->>FW: Detect MQTT interruption / reboot
  FW->>API: GET /api/device-open/commands/status?imei=...
  API->>DB: Summarize command state counts
  DB-->>API: statusCounts + retry posture
  API-->>FW: 200 JSON status

  FW->>API: GET /api/device-open/commands/history?imei=...&limit=20
  API->>DB: Fetch recent commands
  DB-->>API: commands[] + nextCursor
  API-->>FW: 200 JSON commands

  FW->>FW: Execute any unprocessed commands
  FW->>API: (normal path) Publish ack/resp via MQTT after reconnect
